cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with hand pose estimation from a single depth image. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as hand pose estimation is important for human-robot interaction. The use of deep learning methods suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the exploration of different training strategies could suggest that it belongs to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
